### ğŸ§¬ Kernel Exploits (Old Kernel Abuse)

- [ ]  `uname -a` â€” Check for old vulnerable kernels.
- [ ] Searchsploit: `searchsploit linux kernel [version]`
- [ ] If vulnerable: Download exploit, compile on your box, transfer payload, run carefully.

âœ… _Pro Tip_: ONLY kernel exploit if itâ€™s cleanly vulnerable and no easier path exists!

